Document Status
This is the detailed production design document. All values and rules are subject to simulation validation and certification feedback. Any changes must be documented with impact analysis and version bump. The core math is intentionally close to a proven high-performing title; deviations should be deliberate and well-justified.

Revision Notes (v0.7)
v0.7 adds precision around conversion timing and explosion behavior: After a Marked symbol converts to Wild, the new Wild does not explode in the same cascade and participates normally in future cascades. Wording in spawn rules (Sections 3.2 and 5.2) simplified for consistency. Added explicit statement that the reel 3 full Marked stack is applied at the start of each free spin after prior cascades complete. Version history and footers updated to v0.7.

